OL,3,CSchool teacher driving against medical
OL,4,Cadvice killed couple in A66 crash
OL,6,FMatthew Taylor speaks to a friend of
OL,7,FGareth and Patricia Evans who says the
OL,8,Fcouple are deeply missed in their
OL,9,Fcommunity
OL,11,FA primary school teacher has been
OL,12,Fjailed for killing a retired couple
OL,13,Fheading to church after getting behind
OL,14,Fthe wheel against medical advice.
OL,16,FDavid Peter Henderson, 45, who had a
OL,17,Fhistory of blackouts, had previously
OL,18,Fadmitted his driving caused the deaths
OL,19,Fof Gareth and Patricia Evans of High
OL,20,FBrigham, following a two vehicle crash
OL,21,Fon the A66 on 13 February 2023.
