OL,6,FIn the lead up to the fatal collision
OL,7,FHenderson, travelling in a red
OL,8,FVolkswagen Golf, overtook a line of
OL,9,Fcars on the wrong side of a single
OL,10,Fcarriageway stretch of the A66 near
OL,11,FWorkington, in heavy traffic, while
OL,12,Fheading home from work.
OL,14,FThe court heard how Henderson overtook
OL,15,Fa Mazda whose driver recalled a
OL,16,Fblasting horn from the Golf along with
OL,17,F"repetitive and aggressive" headlight
OL,18,Fflashes.
