OL,6,FThat driver believed the defendant
OL,7,Fthen tried to run him off the road
OL,8,Fbefore accelerating away at an
OL,9,Festimated 80-90mph.
OL,11,FHe watched the Golf then make a slow
OL,12,Fand steady movement right, into the
OL,13,Fopposite carriageway between the
OL,14,FBridgefoot and Stainburn roundabouts.
OL,16,FProsecutor Kim Whittlestone told
OL,17,FPreston Crown Court on Monday 17
OL,18,FFebruary the driver recalled seeing an
OL,19,F"explosion" seconds later.
