OL,6,FHenderson was allegedly unconscious as
OL,7,Fhe drove head-on into a blue Renault
OL,8,FClio driven by 68-year-old Patricia
OL,9,FEvans, whose husband Gareth, 70, was a
OL,10,Ffront seat passenger. The couple died
OL,11,Fat the scene.
OL,13,FData recovered from Henderson's
OL,14,Fvehicle airbag suggested there was
OL,15,Flittle to no input, in terms of
OL,16,Fsteering, accelerating or braking, by
OL,17,Fhim in the five seconds prior to
OL,18,Fimpact.
