OL,6,FThe court heard Henderson had been
OL,7,Fsuffering from a heart condition which
OL,8,Fcaused blackouts for over a decade.
OL,10,F"He knew when he got behind the wheel
OL,11,Fof that vehicle, on that day, that his
OL,12,Fmedical condition risked him blacking
OL,13,Fout behind the wheel," said Miss
OL,14,FWhittlestone.
OL,16,F"He had blacked out on two previous
OL,17,Foccasions behind the wheel."
