OL,6,FThe court heard Henderson latterly
OL,7,Ffailed to inform the DVLA of one such
OL,8,Fblackout, in February 2022, and also
OL,9,Fboth that a pacemaker had been fitted
OL,10,Fand that a doctor had advised, in
OL,11,FAugust that year, that he should not
OL,12,Fthen drive until he had been blackout-
OL,13,Ffree for six months.
