OL,6,FIn what a judge called "deceit and
OL,7,Flies", the court was told Henderson
OL,8,Falso falsely told his head teacher, at
OL,9,FSt Mary's, in Salterbeck, that his
OL,10,Flicence had been returned ` it had
OL,11,Fnever been surrendered ` and wrongly
OL,12,Famended his car insurance policy
OL,13,Fdetails with the words "DVLA aware, no
OL,14,Frestrictions".
OL,16,FHenderson, no longer a teacher,
OL,17,Fadmitted two charges of causing death
OL,18,Fby dangerous driving.
