OL,6,FIn an impact statement, their son
OL,7,FRichard, made a direct address to
OL,8,FHenderson, now in a wheelchair as a
OL,9,Fresult of injuries he sustained in the
OL,10,Fcrash.
OL,12,FHe said: "It is impossible to put into
OL,13,Fwords the pain and heartbreak that you
OL,14,Fhave caused, and the devastating loss
OL,15,Fthat we have suffered as a result of
OL,16,Fyour selfish, thoughtless actions.
OL,26,@tD@JOU
