OL,6,F"They were the most kind, generous,
OL,7,Fthoughtful, caring people. They did so
OL,8,Fmuch for us and gave so much to so
OL,9,Fmany others, both within their local
OL,10,Fcommunities and further afield."
OL,12,F"Two beautiful, amazing souls had
OL,13,Feverything taken away, and we didn't
OL,14,Feven get to say goodbye," added Mr
OL,15,FEvans.
OL,17,F"The man who caused this is nothing to
OL,18,Fus. We don't know you. We don't want
OL,19,Fto make our lives about you. We can't
OL,20,Fwait to never have to think of you
OL,21,Fagain and only remember them."
