OL,6,FHenderson, who had no previous
OL,7,Fconvictions, was not a wicked or
OL,8,Fthoughtless man, said his barrister,
OL,10,FMichael Hayton KC, representing
OL,11,FHenderson, said his client had no
OL,12,Fprevious convictions and was not a
OL,13,Fwicked or thoughtless man, but had
OL,14,Fdone a "wicked thing".
OL,16,F"He is, on any other day, a thoroughly
OL,17,Fdecent man," he added. "He has done
OL,18,Fsomething truly awful."
