OL,6,FHenderson was jailed for seven years
OL,7,Fand four months. He will serve two-
OL,8,Fthirds of the sentence before being
OL,9,Feligible for release, when he must
OL,10,Falso then serve a 12-year driving ban.
OL,12,FOf Mr and Mrs Evans, Judge Barker
OL,13,Fsaid: "Their death was, and is, a
OL,14,Ftragedy. Their loss is bitterly felt
OL,15,Fby their family. I know that this
OL,16,Fhearing, although it will come to a
OL,17,Fclose today, will not provide
OL,18,Fcontinued relief for them.
OL,20,F"They are caught in their tragedy and
OL,21,Ftheir grief will continue."
